        "slug": "the-section-map-as-architecture",
        "text": "The section map as architecture. The five parts of *An der Zeitmauer* shown as a building or landscape: Fremde V\u00f6gel as porch, Me\u00dfbare und Schicksalszeit as first hall, Humane Einteilungen as central space, Siderische Einteilungen as observatory, Urgrund und Person as foundation. This is speculative but J\u00fcnger's own architectural vocabulary (houses, chambers, vestibules, windows, walls) invites it."
